toilet%20and%20for%20making%20my%20life%20%20cheerful.%20%0A%3Cimg%20align%3D%22right%22%20vspace%3D%225%22%20hspace%3D%225%22%20width%3D%22112%22%20height%3D%22150%22%3EIn%20my%20life%20I%20often%20have%20diarrhea%20and%20searching%20Toilet.%3Cp%3E%0A%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EA%20standard%20of%20Tokyo%20Toilet%20Map%3C%2Fh2%3E%0A%3Cul%3E%0A%3Cli%3EI%20check%20the%20men's%20toilet.%20Because%20I%20am%20man.%0A%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMainly%20I%20check%20toilet%20at%20stations.%0A%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20may%20be%20women's%20toilet%20version%20with%20my%20wife's%20cooperation.%0A%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20check%20toilet%20for%20who%20do%20whose%20buisiness.%0A%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20collect%20graffiti.%20Because%20it%20is%20fun.%0A%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%0A%3Cp%20align%3D%22right%22%3E%3Ci%3EI'm%20sorry%20for%20my%20poor%20English%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Ca%20href%3D%22index_e.htm%22%3Ereturn%20to%20homepage%3C%2Fa%3E%0A%0A%3C%2Fbody%3E%0A%3C%2Fbody%3E%0A%3C%2Fhtml%3E"
